          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Water and Agriculture Tax Reform Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to permit tax-exempt mutual ditch or irrigation companies to earn income from dispositions of certain real property and stock interests without affecting their tax-exempt status. Requires that such income be used to pay the costs of operations, maintenance, and capital improvements of such a company.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
